messages.messageBody:
on 6/30/02 12:36 PM, John Julian at jsjulian@... wrote:

> Yes - All of my subjects from lists are blank!!

Well that's weird. I restarted the computer and it fixed it for me. Haven't
had a blank one since then. And here I was being miffed at the computer for
being so enigmatic about wanting to be restarted. It should have just
crashed like it usually does ;-)

Are you using Outlook Express? Maybe there was some weird email that reset
something.

Joyce
